24:56.540 --> 24:57.201
She didn't work? She didn't work. She worked from 
the time her first husband died until she married

24:58.362 --> 25:04.610
my father. She worked as a janitor of a little 
school there, a little sophomore school. She took

25:09.797 --> 25:15.144
him washing and did, I suppose, what would be 
maid's work. But she finished that when my father

25:15.765 --> 25:18.328
died. or she quit that, apparently she married my 
father, and didn't work during their marriage.

25:26.481 --> 25:29.525
Now, during the time that he was ill, we were on 
welfare. And this probably explains the reason

25:30.986 --> 25:40.037
I'm a Democrat, and my father was a Roosevelt 
Democrat, because we were held by the Spanish

25:30.986 --> 25:40.037
program. And then she didn't work again until we 
had all left home. We were all, I suppose, trying to

25:45.464 --> 25:48.147
make our ends meet, And she worked for a while at the 
hospital there at home as a cook, this kind of

25:48.650 --> 25:57.239
thing. She remarried after my father died a third 
time, a man named Percy Sanchez, who was of Mexican

25:57.359 --> 26:15.417
descent, but he was born in Colorado, an American, 
