28:34.936 --> 28:42.087
Wyoming's one of the few states I've only been to a 
tiny bit. First of all, were there very many people

28:44.291 --> 28:47.916
of Mexican origin in Wyoming? Yes, uh-huh. Yes, to 
the extent my hometown, I think, probably the time

28:49.979 --> 29:01.758
I was born in 1930, the time I was first conscious 
of, the population probably varied from 4,000 to

28:49.979 --> 29:01.758
5,000 people. Even now, it's only 8,000, I think. 
