42:18.550 --> 42:20.873
tremendous professional opportunity. I enjoyed 
being in the Spanish culture for the first time in

42:20.893 --> 42:25.819
my life. It was very palpable. I enjoyed it. It 
forced me to renovate my own Spanish. I think the

42:34.589 --> 42:44.000
only reservation I had is I had my family with me, 
which were two young sons at the time, and my wife,

42:34.589 --> 42:44.000
who doesn't, you know, she can speak Spanish. She 
doesn't dominate it. And so I was constantly

42:46.499 --> 42:50.465
worried about little niggling details. I think 
had I been there by myself or just she and I there

42:50.505 --> 42:56.353
together, it would have been a much more enjoyable 
experience. But I think that professionally,

42:56.373 --> 43:00.679
intellectually, it really was a marvelous 
experience. But as a family man, as a concerned

43:01.200 --> 43:04.525
father, I wouldn't want to go back there under 
those conditions again. You know, how old were

43:07.570 --> 43:09.513
your sons then? Well, this picture was taken when 
