44:08.824 --> 44:10.427
get it, I had it. So I've always had sort of a

44:10.767 --> 44:17.740
bench for books. I've enjoyed it. And I think this 
had a great deal to do with it. I can't explain where

44:21.146 --> 44:23.210
did this come from. Where did you go to college? I 
